## About

This project uses the [Engram Protocol](https://github.com/ecomxco/engram) for AI memory infrastructure — persistent context across sessions, devices, and agents.

## Getting Started

1. Open this directory in your AI tool of choice
2. The agent will read STATE.md and ENGRAM.md automatically
3. Start brainstorming — all exchanges are logged to ENGRAM-LOG.md

## Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| STATE.md | Current project state (read first every session) |
| ENGRAM.md | Processed summary of all sessions |
| ENGRAM-LOG.md | Raw verbatim log (append-only) |
| DECISIONS.md | Decision log with rationale |
| AGENTS.md | Agent configuration |
| ENGRAM-INDEX.md | Lookup index for targeted log retrieval |
| CLAUDE.md | Agent instructions |
